<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">42倍速算法，42与某数相乘时，如果这个数能被5整除,先把这个数分解成5乘以“几”，再用210乘以这个“几”。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">42×55=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 42×55</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=42×5×11</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=210×11</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2310</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>